    "name": "Sacrifices",
    "steam_appid": 3263710,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Disclaimer: This is a direct PC port of our mobile game Sacrifices. Expect quite a slow pace, and no microtransactions.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/9c2edafb72c62d5a527ac646821e207b.poster.avif?t=1769727332\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/9c2edafb72c62d5a527ac646821e207b.webm?t=1769727332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/9c2edafb72c62d5a527ac646821e207b.mp4?t=1769727332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rule and guide a Mesoamerican village through the adventures of everyday life in the heart of a ruthless jungle!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this god-game-meets-city-builder, you must manage a cute Aztec village and defend it from the dangers lurking in the jungle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn the faith of your followers, and gift them with divine knowledge to rebuild the village that is now in ruins.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage your Aztec village</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gathering food, chopping wood, putting out fires... Life for your villagers isn't always easy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But one thing is for sure: they can't manage without you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/b4fcf6e2e3c0396b1767f93d92c55e10.avif?t=1769727332\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras_big/b4fcf6e2e3c0396b1767f93d92c55e10.avif?t=1769727332 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Answer prayers from your followers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your protégés won't stop asking you for this, or rather that.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a God, use your powers to bring joy and happiness to your flock, or punish them for their insolence!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/705f73f5cf418140467af0ef0d9bae92.avif?t=1769727332\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras_big/705f73f5cf418140467af0ef0d9bae92.avif?t=1769727332 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arm and defend your followers in battle against rival tribes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many dangers lurk in the jungle! And some enemies can't be defeated without your help.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/a1cacdd625bc08ec2e0f2f785e4a9309.poster.avif?t=1769727332\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/a1cacdd625bc08ec2e0f2f785e4a9309.webm?t=1769727332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/a1cacdd625bc08ec2e0f2f785e4a9309.mp4?t=1769727332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craft more than 150 different weapons and outfits</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We thought it was a good amount. What do you think? It's a bit of work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/de35513b0b44f3a4980604da820dd207.poster.avif?t=1769727332\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/de35513b0b44f3a4980604da820dd207.webm?t=1769727332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/de35513b0b44f3a4980604da820dd207.mp4?t=1769727332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Send expeditions through the wild jungle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designate your best people to obtain the many treasures that abound in the surrounding jungle! And you can always negotiate with the traveling merchant - it's less risky.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/31293d1eee680c85e049e3e5cfedde81.poster.avif?t=1769727332\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/31293d1eee680c85e049e3e5cfedde81.webm?t=1769727332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/31293d1eee680c85e049e3e5cfedde81.mp4?t=1769727332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sacrifice your most fervent followers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accumulate precious blood and unlock ever more knowledge by sacrificing the most pious villagers in your honor! We promise, they won't hold it against you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/a28d709ce98e73339cba4c8b7163c00d.avif?t=1769727332\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras_big/a28d709ce98e73339cba4c8b7163c00d.avif?t=1769727332 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Expand the village</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Regain your lost glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restore your flamboyant city, stone by stone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras/1bcbc94112aa822728dbfbc57e642754.avif?t=1769727332\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263710/extras_big/1bcbc94112aa822728dbfbc57e642754.avif?t=1769727332 width=800 height=445 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
